---
import Layout from '@layouts/Layout.astro'
import Header from '@components/Header.astro'
import Footer from '@components/Footer.astro'
const lastUpdated = 'April 17, 2026'
---

<Layout title="Privacy Policy" description="MLEbotics privacy policy — how we collect, use, and protect your data.">
  <Header />
  <main id="main-content">
    <div class="container legal">
      <div class="legal__header">
        <p class="tag">Legal</p>
        <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
        <p class="legal__meta">Last updated: {lastUpdated}</p>
      </div>

      <div class="legal__body">
        <p>MLEbotics ("we", "us", or "our") operates <strong>mlebotics.com</strong> and related services. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, and protect your information when you use our website and products.</p>

        <h2>1. Information We Collect</h2>
        <h3>Information you provide directly</h3>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>Email address</strong> — when you join our waitlist or contact us.</li>
          <li><strong>Messages</strong> — when you use the community chat widget.</li>
        </ul>
        <h3>Information collected automatically</h3>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>Usage data</strong> — pages visited, time on page, referrer URL, browser type, and device type, collected via privacy-respecting analytics.</li>
          <li><strong>Log data</strong> — IP address, access times, and error logs collected by our hosting provider (Vercel).</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>2. How We Use Your Information</h2>
        <ul>
          <li>To send you product updates, release notes, and early-access invitations (only if you opted in).</li>
          <li>To improve our website and products based on usage patterns.</li>
          <li>To diagnose and fix technical issues.</li>
          <li>To respond to your messages or inquiries.</li>
        </ul>
        <p>We do <strong>not</strong> sell, rent, or share your personal data with third parties for advertising purposes.</p>

        <h2>3. Third-Party Services</h2>
        <p>Our website and apps may use the following third-party services, each with their own privacy policies:</p>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>Vercel</strong> — hosting and edge functions (<a href="https://vercel.com/legal/privacy-policy" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">privacy policy</a>)</li>
          <li><strong>Firebase / Google</strong> — authentication, database, and analytics (<a href="https://firebase.google.com/support/privacy" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">privacy policy</a>)</li>
          <li><strong>Google Fonts</strong> — font delivery</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>4. Cookies</h2>
        <p>We use minimal cookies required for site functionality. We do not use tracking or advertising cookies. You can control cookies through your browser settings.</p>

        <h2>5. Data Retention</h2>
        <p>We retain your email address until you request removal. Usage analytics are retained in aggregate, anonymised form. You may request deletion of your data at any time by emailing us.</p>

        <h2>6. Your Rights</h2>
        <p>Depending on your jurisdiction, you may have the right to:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Access the personal data we hold about you.</li>
          <li>Request correction or deletion of your data.</li>
          <li>Withdraw consent at any time (e.g., unsubscribe from emails).</li>
          <li>Lodge a complaint with your local data protection authority.</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>7. Security</h2>
        <p>We use industry-standard security measures including HTTPS, Firebase security rules, and access controls. However, no method of transmission over the internet is 100% secure.</p>

        <h2>8. Children's Privacy</h2>
        <p>Our services are not directed to children under 13. We do not knowingly collect personal information from children.</p>

        <h2>9. Changes to This Policy</h2>
        <p>We may update this policy periodically. We will notify users of significant changes by updating the date at the top of this page.</p>

        <h2>10. Contact</h2>
        <p>Questions about this policy? Contact us at <a href="mailto:eddie@mlebotics.com">eddie@mlebotics.com</a>.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>
  <Footer />
</Layout>

<style>
  .legal {
    max-width: 760px;
    padding-top: 5rem;
    padding-bottom: 6rem;
  }
  .legal__header { margin-bottom: 3rem; }
  .legal__header h1 {
    font-size: clamp(1.8rem, 4vw, 2.6rem);
    font-weight: 700;
    color: #fff;
    margin-bottom: .5rem;
  }
  .legal__meta { font-size: .8rem; color: var(--muted); }
  .legal__body { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 1.25rem; }
  .legal__body p { font-size: .95rem; color: #94a3b8; line-height: 1.8; }
  .legal__body h2 {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: #fff;
    margin-top: 1.5rem;
    padding-bottom: .5rem;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
  }
  .legal__body h3 { font-size: .95rem; font-weight: 600; color: #cbd5e1; }
  .legal__body ul {
    padding-left: 1.5rem;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: .4rem;
  }
  .legal__body li { font-size: .95rem; color: #94a3b8; line-height: 1.7; }
  .legal__body a { color: var(--cyan); text-decoration: none; }
  .legal__body a:hover { text-decoration: underline; }
  .legal__body strong { color: #e2e8f0; }
</style>
